Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Streck UA-Cellular Complete, a quality control material for evaluating accuracy and precision of urinalysis instruments measuring sediment and chemistry parameters
Indications for Use Summary: UA-Cellular Complete is an assayed chemistry and cellular urine control for evaluating the accuracy and precision of methods on multiple automated urinalysis platforms and manual testing, including sediment and chemistry parameters.
